{"tid":396304,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ViuTV] 星期一 2230-2300 雙商","createTime":"2017-09-11T14:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T00:12:29.000Z","uid":33798,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"357f015cc7102c928f121528f5d2faf16a48c003","tid":396304,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:28:29.000Z","msg":"近年愈來愈多人創業，當中不少是情侶檔，兩口子走在一起，一同追夢，互相扶持，絕對是不少人追求的人生經歷。不過事實上「雙」和「商」在一起充滿矛盾，可以並存嗎？ViuTV99台全新實況娛樂節目《雙商》，以「一間小店，一盤生意，一段感情。」為主題，與觀眾一同探討「愛情」和「事業」兩個圈子互相交錯時，主角的人生觀驗和他們獨有的生意哲學。每集節目會邀請藝人以短劇方式，帶出去飾演該集真實個案的情侶主角營商時最深刻的回憶和生意哲學。節目更會透過與真實個案的主角訪問和派發小任務，呈現他們獨有的生意哲學和愛情態度，考驗他們之間在愛情和事業中的默契。<br />\n<br />\n吵架吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89424a62553ac4cd528f04efd244bf441847c34","tid":396304,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:33:01.000Z","msg":"短劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8f83c8c139c8c2050a61d4cda946d24dcfacc5","tid":396304,"uid":72466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"應該用短劇做open？"},{"pid":"bcd4594d914fc0ec2374816e1295ecdbe4fa3258","tid":396304,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"拍拖一年就一齊開舖都幾危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b59f79b039c7233a2dfc6903e4bd729535cbcc","tid":396304,"uid":84951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:38:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1457c8530d2463d81efbb2ad113648e1aa764102","tid":396304,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:39:33.000Z","msg":"又派狗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ef